extendedInfo.description: ONLY app with ALL Sydney traffic cameras!Traffic web cams for commuters in Sydney, AustraliaReady to head home and you want to check the traffic? Live Traffic Sydney is the fastest way to get to the traffic web cams that matter to you. Instead of browsing to a web site and working your way through the menus and map graphics to find a web camera just open Live Traffic Sydney on your android and go straight to the camera you want with one click. Navigate through the other cameras along your route, in order, with a simple Next button.Should I stay or should I go?The traffic is slowing to a crawl. Is it going to clear quickly or is it time to bail and find a better route? Open Live Traffic Sydney, select the nearest camera with one click and then navigate through the web cams along your route to see how far the congestion continues.Cameras are maintained by Roads and Traffic Authority (RTA). Individual cameras may be inoperative due to weather conditions or maintenance requirements.Keywords: Traffic camera sydney, traffic cams sydney, Sydney Traffic Cameras, web cameras sydney, traffic sydney
